		<title>The Top 20 Tips From Our Blog This Year: Nuances &#038; Tricks Too Good to Miss</title>
		<link>https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2022/12/12/top-marketing-tips</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Kristen McCormick]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Mon, 12 Dec 2022 14:44:56 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[WordStream]]></category>
